To configure a new broker:
- copy sample configuration directory
- edit activemq.env to set autostart to yes (if needed)
- edit activemq.env to set a non-root user
- edit config.properties to set a broker name and TCP port
- edit config.properties to set any relevant parameter
- edit jetty.xml to set a TCP (HTTP) port
- edit jetty-realm.properties to change the webadmin login/passwd
